English:
Bitplane is the only bi-monthly italian printed Amiga magazine with CD Rom.
It has 64 pages packed with previews, reviews, tutorials and much more.
Here you can find a sample of the cover and a list of the contents of issue 2.
The magazine can be bought directly from us at 7,75 euros + shipping costs
or you can subscribe at 30.20 euros for 6 months subscription or 60,40 for 12 
months including postage and packing. 
Please e-mail at: info@bitplane.it

